This folder contains code for the following components:
1. Clustering and characterization of the galaxy data using MtFAD and MOBSynC (MBC-GAMAData.R);
2. The MtFAD algorithm for the t-mixture of group-specific factor analysers (mtfad.R);
3. A 3D visualization function for simple clusters (starcoord3d.R);
4. A pairwise overlap map function (utilis.R);
5. A GDT function for Gaussianizing the composite clusters (Gtrans-sync.R).
